articles.title: No more miners trapped underground in South Africa, volunteers say - BBC.com
articles.description: At least 78 bodies and more than 200 survivors have been pulled out of a mine since Monday.
articles.content:
No more illegal miners are believed to be trapped underground at a gold mine in South Africa, volunteers working with rescue teams have said.
